    <string name="how_to_read_map_desc" formatted="false">Shows Total Fuel Trim (STFT + LTFT)\n🟢 Green (±5%) = Perfect\n🔴 Red (Negative) = Rich (Reduce fuel)\n🔵 Blue (Positive) = Lean (Add fuel)\n\nCELL LOCK &amp; HIT COUNTER:\nCells start transparent. Hold steady RPM/MAP to collect data. Opacity increases with hits.\nx20 hits = Locked (Gold Border).\n\nDEVIATION: Shows (LPG/CNG - Petrol).\n+ means LPG is Lean. - means LPG is Rich. Aim for 0%.\n\nTUNE ASSIST: Shows exact % correction for your LPG map (Exportable to CSV).\n\n* Note: To use Tune Assist or Deviation, you must collect BOTH Petrol and LPG data first!</string>
